        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "WolfGANG Sessions #28 | A Wild Night of Chamber Music |  Sat, Mar 21, 2026, 9:00 pm | Club SAW"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
